  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nRight now before the 1.10 release is the best timing to do breaking changes.\r\nMoving the simulated backend from `accounts/abi/bind/simulated` to either `/simulated` or maybe `tests/simulated` would be good.\r\nAlso moving the `accounts/abi/bind` to `abi/bind/` would be a good change imo, as `abi` doesn't have anything to do with accounts.\r\n\r\n# Implications\r\nMoving the packages would have implications for all depending projects as they would have to update their dependencies to reflect the new paths.",
